products.full_description:
Rivon Herbal Hair Darkening Dye contains an advanced technological formula of natural herbal extracts that easily clean and condition hair while darkening grey hair simultaneously. It contains various herbal extracts such as Noni, Wild Ginseng, Ganoderma Lucidum, Olive Oil, Aloe Vera and Ayurvedic Herbs. This combination instantly transforms and darkens hair within minutes. The herbal mixture absorbs rapidly and effectively nourishes and protects hair. The combination of ingredients help promote hair growth and prevent hair loss. It is easily applied and results in natural colored, lustrous and beautiful hair.For best results, use twice a month. DIRECTIONS:

1. Put on a pair of gloves;

2. Wet the hair and wipe off most of the water on the hair;

3. Tear open the sachet and squeeze the cream into a bowl then mix evenly;

4. Promptly apply the mixture into the hair, massage and soak for 20 mins;
